Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.51,0:00:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you go to Europe together with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.17,0:00:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to study to the point of\Ndoing all those things?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.12,0:00:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, playing the piano on that stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,didn't you enjoy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.30,0:00:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with playing the piano\Nfreely and in the way I enjoy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.87,0:00:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuoka Prefecture, Okawa Town
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.43,0:00:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanpai!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.34,0:00:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time since the whole\Nfamily is here to make a toast like now, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.77,0:00:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been two years since Megumi returns home, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you would return home sooner, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.24,0:00:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope she didn't just play around in Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.18,0:00:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She never had to stay another year in the same grade,\Nwhich means she was doing her best!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.31,0:00:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good, very good!\NVery good, very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Megumi wants\Nto do, next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.02,0:00:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way or that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unless she goes to education school for teaching,\Nshe can't get a usual job in education, can she?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.05,0:01:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore she can't be a kindergarten teacher.\NIt's a certainty that Onechan is our family's bad debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.90,0:01:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bbb...bad debt?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad debt?! What are you talking about!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.13,0:01:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Yoshitaka! Don't say such a thing\Nto your Onechan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.65,0:01:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since a long time ago\Nit is only for Onechan that the money goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.85,0:01:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,paying a lot of money to let her study in\Na music academy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.79,0:01:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the end it can't be used to get a job ,\Nisn't it a complete bad debt??!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.62,0:01:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, what would have been left if\Nwe had taken piano away from Megumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.23,0:01:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if it was a usual University, perhaps she\Nwouldn't be be able to enter...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.11,0:01:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.14,0:01:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she gets a degree from a music academy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.37,0:01:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the society will look at her as an\N"Ojousan who graduates from a music academy"!\N(ojousan/ojousama=a well-bred daughter of a well-to-do family)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.05,0:01:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And who knows, perhaps she can marry\Nsomeone (from an elite family)....
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.91,0:01:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.86,0:01:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi, you won't eat anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.51,0:01:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi-chan..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.51,0:01:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Megumi-chan is not alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.86,0:01:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Originally she's never alright, isn't she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.81,0:01:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking about it, yes she is acting strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.59,0:01:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Megumi returned home, she never plays\Nthe piano, not even once...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:01:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas Concert 2006\NThe Rising Star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.23,0:02:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you wait
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Rising Star's Christmas Concert\NMemorial Set-Menu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-san, do you want to have it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Club House Sandwich and coffee, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.69,0:02:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hai...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.72,0:02:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how was it about that matter with the Conductor?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.10,0:02:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as Chiaki-kun has selected, I went to\Nhave a talk with Matsuda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's very much interested in Rising Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.73,0:02:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the Christmas Concert will be your\Nlast conducting in Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.01,0:02:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Itadakimasu!\N(=a greeting before you eat)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.30,0:02:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuma-san
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.14,0:02:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for various things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.07,0:02:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The information you gave has been a great help too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.53,0:02:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.83,0:02:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...why did you help us a lot to this extent?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I feel glad that you have trust in\Nmy ability....but why do you always help....\NEh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I feel glad that you have trust in\Nmy ability....but why do you always help....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.73,0:02:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Brahms, who had excellent people\Nwith the instructor roles like Cossel and Joseph,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for a musician to have his name written in history,\Nhe doesn't only needs talent,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.09,0:02:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he also needs an important "deai" with another.\N(=meet a new friend, partner, etc)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:03:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also wish to be one of the persons with such a role.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.30,0:03:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuma-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take good care of your "deai" with me too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.90,0:03:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.36,0:03:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deadline for your draft is 30 minutes ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...Hai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot...hot....it's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he was younger, Sakuma-san also aimed\Nto be a musician, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either to be a pianist, or a conductor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Chiaki-kun now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.06,0:03:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"For a musician to have his name written in history,\Nhe doesn't only needs talent,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.78,0:03:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he also needs an important "deai" with another."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then does it mean that he didn't get a good chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.37,0:03:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. It seems that he has no talent in music.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why all the more....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,..he can't overlook a person, who despite having\Nthe talent, is making it a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.34,0:03:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:04:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,praying for the efforts of all the new members,\Nand for the success of the Christmas Concert...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ah, I almost forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.50,0:04:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,..and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.21,0:04:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in addition also praying for ..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.81,0:04:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the future activities of Chiaki who's going to\Ngo abroad...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KANPAI!\NKanpai!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.11,0:04:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-Sama, umm....thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for inviting us here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't forgotten us, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no, it's because you also sent me the\Ndemo-tape for the audition...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.54,0:04:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Moe-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We passed the audition for this Oke using\Nour own power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.69,0:04:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now there's no need for us to beg\NChiaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys have good points too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder you were selected as the members\Nfor Stresemann's Oke
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your expression was rich, and also interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And on top of that, you're also cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.64,0:04:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I have your cell phone numbers?\NEh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I have your cell phone numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.14,0:04:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to my surprise, everybody really becomes\Nso skillful now, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.52,0:04:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-Sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.65,0:04:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru is happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moe too!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also happy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:04:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me who's happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone! Gimme a rope!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!\NThanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masumi-chan, you're wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.48,0:05:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-kun, have you decided which country\Nyou're going to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, well....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Kuroki-kun? Sooner or later\Nyou'll study abroad too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. At the beginning of next year,\NI plan to take the exams for a school abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ehh...so the Samurai is going to study abroad too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chiaki....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did find a new conductor, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as he'll be your replacement,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you if he's not someone\Nwhom everybody can accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally this day has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.99,0:05:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's no Chiaki Shinichi,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's only ONE person who can\Nconduct this Oke!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.25,0:05:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!! The secondly famous in this Academy....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.96,0:05:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda Yukihisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.13,0:05:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was with Paris Orchestra until last year,\Nand now he's conducting M Philharmony in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda-Sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.80,0:05:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a young and number-one conductor, isn't he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:05:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're so overjoyed, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Matsuda-san, he has a career already,\Nour audience will increase!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.59,0:06:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my job has finished now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.51,0:06:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has finished...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all of it..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to move out of this place too,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.04,0:06:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to start with the preparation to go abroad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.42,0:06:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything....will have to be packed away...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the power is off, it cannot connect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No use! Nodame....it can't connect at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, is she still feeling down?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.12,0:07:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Nodame-chan won't come to see\Nour Christmas Concert...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! You mean Chiaki-kun's girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.39,0:07:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously I'll kill you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't kill her!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aaaaahhhh!\NHey, don't kill her!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aaaaahhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talking about Nodame-chan....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.41,0:07:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with playing the piano freely,\Nin the way I enjoy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be it good or not..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't listen to your piano anymore, can I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.65,0:07:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, is it Chiaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From this year, we start selling Christmas Cake\Nin our restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already took the order!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.48,0:07:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually Nodame-chan promised to pick it up,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but as she suddenly had to return to her home,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.46,0:07:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she told me to give it to Chiaki-san as a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.56,0:07:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said her home was in Okawa City, Fukuoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said it was a metropolitan,\Nquite a big city, it seems....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.57,0:08:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, and so concerning the delivery...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki, I cancel the practice for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.18,0:08:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.06,0:08:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Kiyora...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she got mad because there's no\Noff-day until Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haaaaa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all, bye for now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the delivery!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well...Ck!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't contact her by cell phone,\Nthen Nodame's home phone number...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just home address!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.88,0:08:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This parent!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.11,0:08:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a musician to have his name written in history,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he doesn't only needs talent,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he also needs an important "deai" with another.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also wish to be one of the persons with such a role.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:09:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to be such a person??
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if I have nothing better to do, going to Kyushu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, why do I have to do to this extent..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Narita Airport, please.\NHai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll go by Shinkansen (Bullet Train)..\NHai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Tokyo Station, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.13,0:09:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year 2007!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From S-Projects
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame Cantabile\NLast Lesson
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,http://s-projects.org
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.87,0:09:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not re-distribute at other places.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.68,0:09:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ara, isn't it Megumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.99,0:09:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:09:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's tuned..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.42,0:11:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okawa..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okawa Station..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no Okawa Station!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind!\NToo troublesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please go to this address!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here uninvited all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how can I persuade her?\N"Purigorota Strap Series"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.16,0:12:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew she has no interest in being\Na professional
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also knew that she will strongly reject\Nif being forced...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.38,0:12:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,however, only to me.....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you go to Europe together with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that if I said those words,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she would certainly follow me (to Europe)....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to study to the point\Nof doing all those things?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.19,0:12:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I.....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much courage do you think I've gathered\Njust to say those words?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.02,0:13:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To say that I want to bring along such a hentai with me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.02,0:13:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good, very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a piece you learned at school, isn't it?\NWhat a good piece is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is Schubert.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shubert?\NEhhh.....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.77,0:13:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the piece I played at the Competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Competition...it's a tournament for piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waaahhh....Megumi in tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:14:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I failed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then?\NWas the tournament enjoyable?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because the audience...they clapped\Ntheir hands a lot for me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it was in the First Stage,\Nbut I was very surprised...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.83,0:14:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I was told to fix my neguse hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.25,0:14:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haaaaaahhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I wasn't good with Schubert,\Nyet I could finally played it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he supported me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi always wore beautiful dresses too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.69,0:14:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fare: 5470 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saga Prefecture\NKiyama town
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:14:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to Saga
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious Saga Seaweed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you don't make a mistake\Nwith where you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where I want to go is Okawa City in\NFukuoka Prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.89,0:15:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, right, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.66,0:15:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Okawa City, it's mostly in Saga.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it is not a metropolitan, a big city?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it wouldn't be that far because\Nit's in a city in Fukuoka
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The number you called is in a place unreachable.\NIt could be turned off....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected, it is still off..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, it is still in off condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.05,0:15:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,23 mails?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12/19 This is Eto\N12/19 It's Eto!\N12/9 Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12/19 Come out!\N12/19 Important notice!\N12/19 Told you it's Eto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.53,0:15:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12/20 Come out I said!\N12/20 This is Eto Kozo.\N12/20 Mail from Eto
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12/20 This is Eto Sensei\N12/20 There's no time left!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All from Eto Sensei..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12/20 From Eto to Noda\N12/20 This is Ex-Harisen\N12/20 From Eto
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12/20 We ate crabs together, didn't we?\N12/21 This is Eto Kozo, I said!\N12/21 What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12/21 It's Eto, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.91,0:15:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12/21 I beg you, please come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.41,0:15:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12/21 Puri Gorota NEWS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.06,0:15:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puri Gorota NEWS, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.06,0:15:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Eto, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyabo..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Recommended by Auclair Sensei, who was\Na Jury in that Competition,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:16:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sent a school application form to\NConservatoire De Paris
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.91,0:16:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The exams will be in February
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go, hurry up contact me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi! Please buy nira for me!\N(=garlic leeks)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.81,0:16:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Chiaki-Sama is in Kyushu right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unexpectedly Ryuuchan has something good in you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's for the sake of my best friend\Nand soul mate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover if Nodame's not here, there's no one\Nto test the taste of the new-menu,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and my Dad is inconvenienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuutaro..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masumi-chan yourself, are you okay with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.92,0:16:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Letting Chiaki go under your very eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the start, just looking at him\Nis the most I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.34,0:16:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I can be as close to Chiaki-Sama as now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.49,0:16:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is also thanks to Nodame, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.89,0:16:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we have no practice, we really have nothing\Nelse to do, have we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, as expected, they are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:17:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, all of you, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hashimoto-kun and the others said let's practice\Ntogether by ourselves today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.90,0:17:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Christmas Concert will be Chiaki's\Nlast performance in Japan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only thing we can do\Nfor him, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, all of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up to now we're indebted to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,therefore for the last performance we should\Nat least perform well to see him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Mine's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, he's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Kuroki-kun and friends too? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.71,0:17:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in, come in!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.61,0:17:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow we can't relax...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if suddenly there's no practice, we have\Nno other things to do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK! Let's practice then!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.27,0:17:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YES!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.14,0:17:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,fare: 16.270 yen\N(LOL, very expensive, haha)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.69,0:17:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What metropolitan?? Always lying, always!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.27,0:17:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From some rumours...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today Tanioka Sensei and his family went to...\NLiar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today Tanioka Sensei and his family went to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mexico...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:17:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that she...(also lied)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:18:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I participated in the Competition\Nbecause of the prize money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.32,0:18:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the desire to have the money\Nto play around!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And at that time too,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she also diverted her eyes away...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the competition..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,playing the piano on the stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.91,0:18:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,really, didn't you enjoy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.79,0:18:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.92,0:18:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,actually....
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.07,0:18:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda Megumi
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it Nodame?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's Nodame.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.35,0:18:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? I'm in my hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Senpai is still in Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.33,0:18:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now where do you think I....
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,..am..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.11,0:18:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.28,0:18:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame decided to study abroad too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.41,0:18:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mukya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:18:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Opposite direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:18:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Turn!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind, stop here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oppose? Senpai opposes to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.42,0:19:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Senpai yourself said that for Nodame,\Nthe school abroad is more suitable...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About that..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really serious when saying it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.95,0:19:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.31,0:19:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a message from Eto Sensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.09,0:19:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he told me that a gentleman called Auclair-san\Nrecommended me to a school over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In what country will your school be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.04,0:19:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm....France!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.22,0:19:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,France? Conservatoire?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.68,0:19:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But from now on I will still have to take an exam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.34,0:19:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it might be a different country from where\NSenpai is going to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.46,0:19:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Nodame will do my best studying piano!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.82,0:19:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do that, then someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just like Milch and Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:20:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,perhaps I can perform a concerto on\Nthe same stage as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki Senpai will be the Conductor,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame will play the piano,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.36,0:20:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,performing in Philadelphia Orchestra.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That performance will be a great success,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and from all over the world there will come requests\Nfor Senpai and Nodame, the Golden Pair, to perform!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.81,0:20:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Performing Rhapsody In Blue with New York\NPhilharmonic is also good, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And performing with Senpai, what about\Ndoing Violin Sonata too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.50,0:20:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are still a lot of other things...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.23,0:20:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that are enjoyable...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.12,0:20:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About those things..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,say it only after you pass the exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.74,0:20:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You MUST pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to Europe together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.62,0:21:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you reject Ore-sama again for the second time,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,certainly I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.19,0:21:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm....
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.96,0:21:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing there??! On such a place???
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.27,0:21:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ack! Daddy!!\NAheeem..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.87,0:22:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heeeheee.....
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.47,0:22:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuuuuuu.....
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.58,0:22:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Studying abroad???!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.09,0:22:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's why, please give me your\Ninsurance-for-the-aged money!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.13,0:22:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! No such thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.36,0:22:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day the seaweed machine\Nexploded too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.40,0:22:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.84,0:22:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.90,0:22:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's about the funds for studying abroad,\Nthere are foundations which can give support,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.18,0:22:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it won't be a problem, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.71,0:22:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it won't be a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.50,0:22:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.23,0:22:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it will be fine. Especially because she\Nis recommended by someone over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.92,0:22:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as she can pass the exam....
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.27,0:22:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!\NGreat!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.49,0:22:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.50,0:22:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So your route is decided already!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.87,0:22:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you'll still be studying!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.98,0:22:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good, that's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.69,0:22:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good, but you.... dokon no hito?\N(=who are you, where from?)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.23,0:22:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.83,0:22:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dokon???\N(He didn't understand)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.11,0:22:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Chiaki Shinichi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.48,0:22:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyaaahaaa...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.34,0:22:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he Megumi's boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.52,0:22:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyahaaa!! Boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.09,0:22:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lie! It's impossible that she\Ncan have a handsome boyfriend like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:22:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's a lie, it's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.63,0:22:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a friend from the same school!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:22:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.84,0:22:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what were you trying to do\Nat the riverbed??
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.36,0:23:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was...umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.59,0:23:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's like when a football player hugged another\Nplayer of the same team when a goal was made,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.65,0:23:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was no deeper meaning..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.85,0:23:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hugged you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.05,0:23:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haauuunn...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.02,0:23:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!!!\NHaauuunn...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.05,0:23:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.94,0:23:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WELL DONE, Megumi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ne-chan, GOAL IN!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...no!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.27,0:23:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said let's go to Europe together...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.03,0:23:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said if I rejected him a second time,\Nhe wouldn't forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.36,0:23:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I meant if she rejected my invitation\Nto study together in Europe!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.80,0:23:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you invited her!! And TWICE too!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.08,0:23:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GOAAAALLLL!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.48,0:23:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A boyfriend and studying abroad!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.98,0:23:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, oi! Bring in some sake! (japanese wine)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.75,0:23:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a celebration, a celebration!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.28,0:23:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This family..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.50,0:23:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Embarrassing, embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.34,0:23:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they don't care about where their daughter\Nis going to go, about piano or music?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.82,0:23:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-kun....
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.09,0:23:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today...rest for the night here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.17,0:23:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.96,0:23:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you try my cooking,\NEh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.17,0:23:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you try my cooking,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.51,0:23:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-san!\N(as if Chiaki is his brother-in-law already)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.68,0:23:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-san??
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.23,0:23:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're officially recognized, aren't you?\NHeheemm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.46,0:23:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this way, Nodame became what she is now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.52,0:24:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haa, so beautiful....\Nbut it's cold...brrr...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.18,0:24:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otsukare!\N(greeting for someone after working hard)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.38,0:24:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh! Kiyora!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.03,0:24:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.49,0:24:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you were waiting for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.92,0:24:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.41,0:24:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it unusual for you to be the last one\Nto stay practising?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.01,0:24:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you yourself alright, with playing\NCarmen violin solo?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.75,0:24:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, because it's my favorite piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.77,0:24:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Passionate, lively, dynamic!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.96,0:24:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's a piece that suits Kiyora's violin\Nextremely well.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.47,0:24:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a piece that fits our last performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.77,0:24:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's surely make it a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.88,0:24:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.14,0:24:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.75,0:24:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will do my best in Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.12,0:25:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.28,0:25:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my very best!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.22,0:25:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.75,0:25:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then someday..
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.44,0:25:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you return to Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.15,0:25:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.91,0:25:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll compete with you for the Concert Master!!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.45,0:25:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.95,0:25:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.34,0:25:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Senpai! Grandma said breakfast was ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.99,0:25:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK..
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.69,0:26:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you enter Nodame's room by yourself?\NIt's embarrassing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.74,0:26:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.55,0:26:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ack, Senpai, which country are you going to go?\NHah?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.74,0:26:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ack, Senpai, which country are you going to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.19,0:26:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prague.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.56,0:26:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a house there in which we used to\Nlive in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.86,0:26:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I was thinking either Prague or Paris,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.78,0:26:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,either one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.25,0:26:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I didn't know that you were\Ngoing to go to Paris...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.98,0:26:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Prague near to Paris?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.81,0:26:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.53,0:26:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a distance I can go to your place\Nto eat after school is over?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.22,0:26:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To eat???
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.66,0:26:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's out of the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.62,0:26:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's Japan, it's like from Tokyo to Saga, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.89,0:26:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you think it will take by train??
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.94,0:26:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then what about making it halfway\Nbetween Tokyo and Saga...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.65,0:26:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the two of us living in Osaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.08,0:26:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.21,0:26:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, let's plan the path for the two\Nof us to live together!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.68,0:26:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's from now on that we'll\Npass the happy time together...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.91,0:26:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good, not good!!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.55,0:27:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case you'll soon miss me, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.25,0:27:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover when we were apart, we\Nalready nurtured our love quite enough....
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.99,0:27:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't nurture anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.39,0:27:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did Senpai come here??
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.57,0:27:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To cheer for Fukuoka Daiei Hawks...\N(ex-baseball team from Fukuoka)
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.28,0:27:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mukyaa!\NIt's Softbank Hawks now!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.80,0:27:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, they are not having any match anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.83,0:27:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...to cheer for (Softbank) Camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.55,0:27:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No Camp right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.06,0:27:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You..
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.93,0:27:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than that, piano!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.15,0:27:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.85,0:27:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really practice well?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.83,0:27:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't pass the exam,\Nyou can't go anywhere, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.51,0:27:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know...I have to take the exam..
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.44,0:27:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then play a little now!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.71,0:27:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Play the piece for that previous Competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.83,0:27:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...okay, Chopin's Etudes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.62,0:27:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! Your fingers are not moving properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.10,0:27:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.95,0:27:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could play Schubert well last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.87,0:27:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are as if not my own hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.28,0:27:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ack, game callus!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.63,0:27:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're completely lazing around, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.04,0:28:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyabo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.71,0:28:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.27,0:28:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mukyaa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.97,0:28:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back to Tokyo and have crash training!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.40,0:28:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.72,0:28:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A person who played the piano everyday for long hours..
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.46,0:28:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,hasn't played anymore for days since that Competition...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.15,0:28:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.36,0:28:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, seabream??!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.72,0:28:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otsukare!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.07,0:28:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's big, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.11,0:28:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(seabream is for celebration)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.79,0:28:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, even when there's no time left for the exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.73,0:28:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't hurry to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.04,0:28:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you around in Okawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.59,0:28:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's OK,\N"Okawa the best furniture maker in Japan"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.54,0:28:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your daughter is in critical condition.\N"Okawa Furniture Hall"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.88,0:28:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then just one place!\N"Koga Masao Memorial Hall"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.97,0:28:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ack, Beethoven!\N(Karaoke Pub Beethoven)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.35,0:28:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waaah....mud land! It's the first time I came here!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.37,0:28:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there are mudskippers?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.16,0:28:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.44,0:28:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi! We don't have time!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.78,0:28:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Chiaki-kun, Chiaki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.43,0:28:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a telescope here! I'll take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.19,0:28:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hai
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.41,0:28:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We take our seaweeds over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.66,0:29:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here, take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.16,0:29:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't say: "Musume wo tanomu"\N(Take good care of my daughter, meaning to marry her)
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.91,0:29:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.54,0:29:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will she be really alright?\NStudying abroad?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.97,0:29:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.72,0:29:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi started learning the piano when\Nshe was 5 year old.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.47,0:29:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was when I was still working in an office in Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.86,0:29:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a music academy ojousan in the neighbourhood,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.25,0:29:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could always hear the sounds of the piano...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.32,0:29:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi loves the piano very much
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.82,0:29:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so she often visited her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.47,0:30:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In just a short time,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.13,0:30:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that ojousan came with her face turning pale,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.19,0:30:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okasan!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.14,0:30:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better to have this child learn piano\Nfrom a proper teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.75,0:30:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, we enrolled her to a piano classroom\Ntaught by a famous piano teacher in our neighbourhood.\N"Hanasakura Piano Classroom"
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.02,0:30:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then..again very soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.65,0:30:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take this child as soon as\Npossible abroad!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.61,0:30:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, around that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.94,0:30:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi's condition began to become strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.90,0:30:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The teacher gave extremely strict lesson
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.79,0:30:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi didn't like going to the piano classroom anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.68,0:30:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day that incident happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.68,0:30:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This hand is wrong! This hand!!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.41,0:30:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This hand is bad!..
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.43,0:30:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.34,0:31:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although the teacher apologized many many times,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.25,0:31:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from that day Megumi hardly played the\Npiano anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.98,0:31:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just like she was, before yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.41,0:31:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Megumi suitable for this (music) world?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.65,0:31:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be a professional pianist....
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.19,0:31:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is not only to play the piano as one enjoys it, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.25,0:31:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A wound....inflicted in childhood..
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.66,0:31:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.54,0:32:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, she's still playing the piano, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.58,0:32:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.14,0:32:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,regardless the teacher is strict or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.30,0:32:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if one is no good, he will be no good,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.95,0:32:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if one wants to be a professional pianist,\Nit doesn't mean he can become one...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.91,0:32:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it is this kind of world.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.14,0:32:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether we will succeed or not,\Nwe have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.94,0:32:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither I nor she know..
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.60,0:32:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But..
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.51,0:32:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really love her piano very much!\N(READ: I love her very much)
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.11,0:32:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi-kun the idiot!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.89,0:32:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the one idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.58,0:32:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...you love (her) so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.18,0:32:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.79,0:32:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My son!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.59,0:32:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hai!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.59,0:32:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My son!!! MY SON!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.04,0:32:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.70,0:32:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tadaima!!!\N(=I come home)
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.77,0:33:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ordered a lot of osushi, please help yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.96,0:33:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can drink a lot of sake too!!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.35,0:33:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-kun drank all of it yesterday, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.73,0:33:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's strong at drinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.80,0:33:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he's strong! Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.97,0:33:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why..
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.94,0:33:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I here again..
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.87,0:33:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on top of it..
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.12,0:33:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,kotatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.55,0:33:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gyouzas are ready!\N(=chinese dumplings)
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.83,0:33:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New creation seaweeds gyouza completed!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.68,0:33:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of Yokkun!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.27,0:33:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They look really delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.51,0:33:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made them for the other employees in my part-time job !
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.97,0:33:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-kun, Chiaki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.79,0:33:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raa yu ready?\N(raa yu= sesame oil with hot chili)
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.31,0:33:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Undoubtedly here is...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.34,0:33:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the hot bed where Nodame grew up...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.06,0:33:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.80,0:33:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my new dress, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.71,0:33:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finished making it today, it's a new\Ncreation for spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.10,0:33:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's released!\NMode Salon Youko!!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.62,0:33:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah right!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.16,0:33:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make some clothes for Chiaki-kun too!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.56,0:33:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.50,0:34:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, perhaps it should\Nbe a white shirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.03,0:34:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Formal! It should be formal, Youko!!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.94,0:34:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The size....
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.90,0:34:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXCUSE ME!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.54,0:34:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame...matashita!!\NNodame will measure his matashita!!\N(=from crotch down the legs)
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.24,0:34:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perverts!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.96,0:34:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good that I will be going to Prague!!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.13,0:34:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.98,0:34:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...DEFINITELY I'm not going to go to France!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.40,0:34:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heeh? Masayuki-san moved to Prague?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.43,0:34:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the problem, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.70,0:34:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi hates nothing more than being said\Nthat he was his father's nanahikari...\N(=has no ability but riding on his father's reputation)
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.20,0:34:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't go to the same Prague
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.50,0:34:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.27,0:34:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah right! What about letting him study\Nin Paris, the number-two candidate?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.38,0:34:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paris?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.94,0:34:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.75,0:34:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The food is delicious, and fashionable too!\NYes!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.94,0:34:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The food is delicious, and fashionable too!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.44,0:34:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true..Paris!\NThat's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.31,0:34:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ehhhh? Masumi-chan's job in an\Norchestra is decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.33,0:34:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.35,0:34:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I passed the exam for New Metropolitan\NPhilharmonic!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.62,0:34:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I be... a genius?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.59,0:35:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, it must be because of\Nyour hairstyle...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.13,0:35:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean??!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.58,0:35:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're noisy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.77,0:35:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, what, what??
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.96,0:35:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, everyone!!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.37,0:35:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyabo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.95,0:35:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gather up when you're ready!!\NGyabo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.37,0:35:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gather up when you're ready!!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.38,0:35:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi! It's just a rehearsal, why do we have\Nto wear tuxedos?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.64,0:35:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.71,0:35:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the actual day we'll be too busy\Nwe won't have any time to take photos, will we?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.46,0:35:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Memorial photos!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.32,0:35:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.07,0:35:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please surely succeed abroad, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.46,0:35:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine..
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.26,0:35:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then these memorial photos will sell higher...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.67,0:35:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.54,0:35:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, who will take the photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.68,0:35:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish Nodame had come here wearing more\Nfashionable attires...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.29,0:35:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why only Nodame is out of the photos?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.93,0:35:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi Nodame, will this be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.90,0:35:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everybody perfectly included?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.53,0:35:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.13,0:35:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it beautifully, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.63,0:35:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.23,0:35:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.74,0:36:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, let's pose the Vienna Philharmonic style!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.91,0:36:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vienna Phil...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.92,0:36:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, I'll take it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.78,0:36:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start practising now!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.18,0:36:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.57,0:36:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, you have to practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.33,0:36:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ehh??
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.71,0:36:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyabo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.86,0:36:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.01,0:36:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.75,0:36:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you in Paris!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.04,0:36:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paris?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.53,0:37:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,http://s-projects.org
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.55,0:37:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sarasate
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.02,0:37:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fantasy piece from "Carmen"
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.74,0:37:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was composed by putting together famous\Nmelodies from the opera Carmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.88,0:37:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a difficult piece that requires\Ntranscendent artmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.39,0:37:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,however..
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.57,0:37:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because it's Kiyora, I can entrust it\Nto her with peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.01,0:37:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make an orchestra, with Chiaki-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.83,0:37:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.49,0:37:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you make an orchestra with me,\Nand perform together?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.53,0:37:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She made this orchestra together with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.37,0:37:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She created a place for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.80,0:38:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.36,0:38:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We really worried for you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.15,0:38:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what's that?\NStudying abroad?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.27,0:38:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really surprised, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.65,0:38:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.70,0:38:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite always taking other people's lunch box!!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.23,0:38:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl!!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.42,0:38:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame!!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.99,0:38:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maki-chan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.27,0:38:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame, do your best, okay!!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.94,0:38:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reina-chan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.43,0:38:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.87,0:38:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,well, various interesting happened, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.82,0:38:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, various scary things happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.82,0:38:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't do anything for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.20,0:38:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. That "Fart Exercise" choreography\Nwas excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.01,0:38:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, whether you really couldn't\Ndo anything or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.83,0:38:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we don't know it yet, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.52,0:38:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be able to know it perhaps 10 years\Nlater, or 20 years later...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.57,0:38:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or perhaps even more than that...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.32,0:39:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.68,0:39:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suntory Hall\NChristmas Concert 2006\NR.S Orchestra
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.53,0:39:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.06,0:39:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.43,0:39:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of Miki Kiyora!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.75,0:39:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the new members too!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.29,0:39:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's as Chiaki-kun said...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.11,0:39:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Oke is really evolving!!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.10,0:40:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now, we'll have 20 minutes break.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.27,0:40:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, the other piece will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.59,0:40:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beethoven Symphony no 7!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.05,0:40:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first piece you conducted,\Nin S-Oke!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.73,0:40:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the piece Stresemann said your\Nconducting was no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.00,0:40:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You failed!" right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.25,0:40:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really the last, isn't it...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.92,0:40:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, although I was mad at you all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.53,0:40:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now it was a good memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.65,0:40:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Had there were no Spartan way of practising,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.40,0:40:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we wouldn't have been here now, would we?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.75,0:40:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.80,0:40:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've just taken over my family's bakery,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.48,0:40:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and would have forgotten about music...I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.87,0:40:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've never realized that I loved music this much,\Nand ended it then and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.52,0:40:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Us too...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.95,0:40:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we thought that orchestra and professional\Ndebut was just a dream in a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.39,0:40:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we graduated while giving it all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.65,0:40:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-Sama, even when you are abroad,\Nwe'll always support you,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.05,0:40:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please don't forget us, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.77,0:40:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.75,0:40:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be doing your best for us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.55,0:40:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too, although I feel bad to my father in inaka...\N(=small town, village)
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.81,0:41:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will do my best for a little more here!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.43,0:41:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after I marry, even after I have kids,\NI will keep doing music!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.95,0:41:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please contact us when you return to Japan, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.37,0:41:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.21,0:41:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-Senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.59,0:41:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,definitely I'll continue playing Contrabass,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.58,0:41:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and definitely I'll enter Vienna Philharmonic,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.65,0:41:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,therefore please wait for me in Europe, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.60,0:41:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.00,0:41:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's you, I believe that even abroad,\Nyou will certainly succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.03,0:41:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet again in spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.95,0:41:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.59,0:41:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, be careful with your relationships\Nwith women,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.56,0:41:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because the ladies over there are quite\Npassionate in many things, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.36,0:41:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me know when you make a\Nprofessional debut,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.47,0:41:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can consult with me concerning\Naccounting matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.38,0:41:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, it had been a while since I last met\Na stimulating friend like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.61,0:41:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow it sounds like a graduation\Nceremony, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.35,0:42:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this orchestra
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.26,0:42:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also love Matsuda-san\N(=the new conductor)
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.66,0:42:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But....
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.59,0:42:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love Chiaki-kun...the BEST!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.24,0:42:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-Sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.36,0:42:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you please pardon me, for my\Nnumerous impoliteness thus far.\N(he's using high and polite Japanese)
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.99,0:42:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and also...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.63,0:42:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sincerely, thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.99,0:42:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treasure those many memories in my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.71,0:42:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From Chiaki-Sama, today Okuyama Masumi will gra...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.05,0:42:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, as I thought, I can't graduate from you!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.94,0:42:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.10,0:42:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm reaaally glad that I met Chiaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.45,0:42:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's for me to say..
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.75,0:42:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some day in the future..
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.40,0:42:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to be entrusted again as the\NConcert Master by Chiaki-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.56,0:42:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll grow to be better too.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.66,0:43:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best together.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.80,0:43:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.28,0:43:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely....
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.62,0:43:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with these same members,\Nlet's do an Oke again!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.81,0:43:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Ryuu-chan, say something too!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.81,0:43:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll write letters to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.26,0:43:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it mail instead!\N(=cell phone or computer mails)
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.47,0:43:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heeeh??
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.02,0:43:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah right! Well, usually people send snail mails...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.64,0:43:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Ookouchi Mamoru is crying too)
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.06,0:43:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,usual snail mails are expensive, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.02,0:43:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame-chan! Let's go to gokon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.35,0:43:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Milch!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.81,0:43:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.68,0:43:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you came for us before the last piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.16,0:43:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please see Chiaki-Senpai! The others will\Ncertainly be very glad to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.52,0:44:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.52,0:44:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.63,0:44:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's Chiaki, there will be no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.95,0:44:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Milch...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.15,0:44:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame too, I am now ready to face\Nmusic seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.34,0:44:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.70,0:44:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame-chan do it
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.30,0:44:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in Nodame-chan's own style!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.48,0:44:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.67,0:44:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hai!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.61,0:44:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.57,0:44:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to enjoy music!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.27,0:44:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ALRIGHT!!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.86,0:44:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.18,0:45:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every year, although so many music academy\Nstudents graduate,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.21,0:45:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the number of professional Oke members\Nare limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.39,0:45:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they have real ability,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.71,0:45:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it doesn't guarantee that they can\Nenter a professional Oke.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.06,0:45:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of them who have to\Nwaste their ability..
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.84,0:45:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.73,0:45:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,their music is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.65,0:45:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very moment now,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.04,0:45:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the happiness of being able to perform music...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.62,0:45:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is overflowing from their spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.60,0:46:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That being able to continue playing music is\Ncertainly not a matter of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.99,0:46:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is one thing..
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.75,0:46:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that they have made me recall....
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.57,0:46:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beethoven Symphony no 7
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.28,0:46:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last piece I conducted\Nwhile being a student in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.90,0:46:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.50,0:47:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the piece that I first conducted in an orchestra...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.04,0:47:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.38,0:47:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also feel that something will begin\Nagain with this piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.91,0:48:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.41,0:48:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember now! You're Chiaki-Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.56,0:49:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make a mistake in just two measures!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.14,0:49:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyabo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.73,0:49:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.46,0:49:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today you may play it freely as you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.88,0:49:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't allow your transfer to\Nthe Conducting Division!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.52,0:49:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, this person will conduct!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.06,0:49:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-Samaaaa!\NKyaaaaa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.42,0:49:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki..
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.55,0:49:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I....conducting this orchestra?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.33,0:49:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!\NChiaki failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.76,0:49:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Failed? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.98,0:49:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always at the center of attention...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.30,0:49:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always having people relying on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.72,0:49:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could a person like you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.44,0:50:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A person like Senpai won't be able to understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.34,0:50:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this feeling of itchiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.70,0:50:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and this feeling of vexation...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.33,0:50:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use your whole body, to express music!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.19,0:50:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying for you to be engrossed in your music!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.74,0:50:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way to fascinate the audience...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.98,0:50:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's also an important study!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.07,0:50:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More beautifully!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.09,0:50:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More romantically!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.91,0:50:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More painfully!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.84,0:50:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More sexily!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.30,0:50:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if you're in agony!!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.24,0:51:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.03,0:51:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,half-heartedness!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.90,0:51:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to care about A-Oke,\Nor about duel...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.06,0:51:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We S-Oke's first stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.35,0:51:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's enjoy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.25,0:51:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.33,0:53:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon it will be farewell....
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.10,0:53:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must also convey ...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.38,0:53:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my gratitude to all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.97,0:53:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They helped...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.68,0:53:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to change me tremendously!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.37,0:53:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An amazing orchestra!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.33,0:53:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's sing!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.99,0:53:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right to the last note!!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.53,0:53:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The greatest music that we can do now!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.98,0:54:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BRAVO!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.22,0:55:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Eto Sensei! From Big fan Toyotaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.85,0:55:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Tanioka Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.81,0:55:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joeboygo LOVES you, Mayuko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.47,0:55:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for your missing lunch boxes, Maki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.82,0:55:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you are second best, Mamoru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.19,0:55:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be a poet, Takuma-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.54,0:55:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great acting, Hatano-san!\NBest regards to Kassy your hubby!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.33,0:55:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine-Papa, I bought Uraken bowl yesterday!\NThank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.75,0:55:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, we hope your fingers are OK now!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.37,0:55:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How the heck you can speak like that, Takenaka-san???
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.49,0:55:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ueno Juri-chan, best regards from BIG fan Thtl!!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.32,0:55:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year 2007, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.26,0:55:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big big thank you from S-Projects!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.26,0:55:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cantabile Team thanks you all for your support!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.84,0:55:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you again all, in Karei Naru Ichizoku!!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.45,0:55:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wishing you a Happy happy New Year 2007!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.35,0:55:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chibi-chan kawaii desu ne!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.41,0:55:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are cool too!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.16,0:55:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gokurousama deshita!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.00,0:55:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kora! ii kagen ni shiro yo!!\NBut I like your always smiling face!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.10,0:55:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masumi-chan, ganbatte ne!!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.89,0:55:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like your acting too, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.52,0:55:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.70,0:56:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Funny hair but it fits you!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.93,0:56:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,LOL! Funny hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.25,0:56:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're beautiful inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.98,0:56:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good diversions, bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.85,0:56:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-chan and Moe-chan, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.11,0:56:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuroki-kun, you're very cool!! Ganbatte!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.31,0:56:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,LOL, it was short but funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.15,0:56:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiyora, you're cool!!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.54,0:56:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine, I still can't make up my mind,\Nyou or Chiaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.46,0:56:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you to everyone who made\Nthis dorama possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.19,0:56:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to everyone watching this now!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.75,0:56:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.41,0:57:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We love you forever Chiaki and Nodame!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.89,0:57:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We hope to see you two again in\NNodame Cantabile II